{"tid":462933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好討厭個身或頭髮有嘢食味？","createTime":"2017-11-09T04:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T06:42:45.000Z","uid":65563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"593ac2f313ce70fd3feb0ead77d9b66b65e3ff4f","tid":462933,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"話說由細到大我都好憎個身或頭髮有嘢食味，例如:打邊爐味、BBQ味、油煙味、炒栗子味。<br />\n<br />\n食嘅時候喺開心，<br />\n但次次食完邊爐同BBQ都要9秒9返屋企沖涼洗頭，<br />\n有時食嘢地方有油煙味亦都喺，<br />\n所以返工食飯都去無油煙味嘅餐廳，當然有時候同事叫到，我都會去，<br />\n但全日個人都覺得好唔舒服，好想快啲收工返屋企沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n有時候陪媽咪行百貨公司，佢好鐘意睇廚具用品（佢唔識煮飯，只鐘意儲），咁有啲賣鑊嘅地方會煎下嘢，炒下嘢，啲油煙味，我一聞到就會即刻快步離開，然後聞自己啲頭髮睇下有無味。<br />\n<br />\n有時候，我覺得自己對呢方面太神經質，<br />\n但我真係好憎自己身上有食物味，覺得好臭，好污糟。<br />\n就算屋企煮完飯，我都要即刻沖完涼先食。<br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣有呢啲怪僻？"},{"pid":"e6486d9b4937da644e9b4f46519123cd72da0479","tid":462933,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f26e9b26600d4d698944cec2b61f2a44d4ff25b","tid":462933,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"我特登唔沖涼等我可以日索夜索送飯"},{"pid":"14da936205b6e2ea81e86a296cbd0310729a0b18","tid":462933,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"x2<br />\nd人叫我燒烤/韓燒我都會say no，<br />\n尤其夏天，又熱又焗會更加臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬天就好少少，不過都會帶定件衫食完換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f76d4ca5a3ca2e09fb250e21c614b75ec7ee26a","tid":462933,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"仲記得上年8月去大板食大板燒，食完出到黎臭到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻要買件衫換再返酒店沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01123adaa314fe5b032a748dbfff97b50b47f52","tid":462933,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>x2<br />\nd人叫我燒烤/韓燒我都會say no，<br />\n尤其夏天，又熱又焗會更加臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬天就好少少，不過都會帶定件衫食完換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏天真喺不了，屋企開住冷氣電爐燒都會嘅（而家嗰啲爐真喺可以做到勁少油煙），不過食完即沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n冬天出去食就會拎定外套放入膠袋再放袋，怕件外套吸哂味，不過而家都有啲鋪好好，有支噴嘢俾你食完噴香返啲衫。"},{"pid":"ae6f2a17b906a3f75e9fa87bd71051f526419946","tid":462933,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲記得上年8月去大板食大板燒，食完出到黎臭到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻要買件衫換再返酒店沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過，我朋友仲話我太誇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50670f3ae97f193917a601375f319e1da9d768f8","tid":462933,"uid":81598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>x2<br />\nd人叫我燒烤/韓燒我都會say no，<br />\n尤其夏天，又熱又焗會更加臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬天就好少少，不過都會帶定件衫食完換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏天真喺不了，屋企開住冷氣電爐燒都會嘅（而家嗰啲爐真喺可以做到勁少油煙），不過食完即沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n冬天出去食就會拎定外套放入膠袋再放袋，怕件外套吸哂味，不過而家都有啲鋪好好，<span style=\"color: red;\">有支噴嘢俾你食完噴香返啲衫</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以冬天一定唔會著外著食依d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  件外套吸晒d味之後又要著番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一定會帶定香水同止汗濟出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412b30989788da5c394342b1db17126f84cb354d","tid":462933,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"衫都臭埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"55b98fad3e464684624d6b0a2063658593288efb","tid":462933,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說由細到大我都好憎個身或頭髮有嘢食味，例如:<span style=\"color: red;\">打邊爐味、BBQ味、油煙味、炒栗子味</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係, 會好想9秒9換過套衫/沖涼 <br />\n但食物味都不及煙味差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時去完K房/酒吧之後就聞到自己成身煙味個吓真係超憎"},{"pid":"82d7bf17acbd2792c311ac8746765b5c6dc23c10","tid":462933,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"同埋我覺得唔算係怪僻啦, 都係乾淨嘅一種"},{"pid":"e13b450ee6397111638f870ac07a27c823b1be38","tid":462933,"uid":27677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"會避免去某幾間去完頭髮，衫會吸味既餐廳，<br />\n無何避免吸左味就會好想去sasa拎d香水tester噴下先安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時會敏感到聞到隔離個人去過都覺得周身唔自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d1a4e57fd985e18d4732c605aafc33063efdc0","tid":462933,"uid":27677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會避免去某幾間去完頭髮，衫會吸味既餐廳，<br />\n無何避免吸左味就會好想去sasa拎d香水tester噴下先安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時會敏感到聞到隔離個人去過都覺得周身唔自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔離個人去過間餐廳，會聞到係邊一間既油煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b51790b4df5a56ec7a3dd2f1c861625dfc2289","tid":462933,"uid":27677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說由細到大我都好憎個身或頭髮有嘢食味，例如:<span style=\"color: red;\">打邊爐味、BBQ味、油煙味、炒栗子味</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係, 會好想9秒9換過套衫/沖涼 <br />\n但食物味都不及煙味差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時去完K房/酒吧之後就聞到自己成身煙味個吓真係超憎</blockquote><br />\nK房陣陳年煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f42a8177716d3443c40eee51f7742fcdbc078d","tid":462933,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"雞煲味先係最撚臭"},{"pid":"56a5b73615a92b62a2375e2fcbc997f8e2fa059a","tid":462933,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"怪乜撚嘢僻 你不如問邊個鐘意 戇鳩鳩"}]}